---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="AI Operations & Automation" description="We deploy AI systems that automate customer service, order processing, and back-office workflows — running in production without constant oversight.">

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section style="background:linear-gradient(160deg,#03142E 0%,#010A18 100%);padding:48px 24px 40px;text-align:center;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(215,161,61,0.1);">
    <div class="section-eyebrow">AI Operations &amp; Automation</div>
    <h1 style="font-family:var(--font-head);font-weight:700;font-size:clamp(22px,6vw,36px);letter-spacing:-0.01em;color:var(--silver);margin-bottom:10px;">Automate the Work.<br><em style="font-style:normal;color:var(--gold);">Free the Team.</em></h1>
    <p style="font-size:14px;color:var(--silver-dim);line-height:1.6;max-width:440px;margin:0 auto 28px;">We build AI systems that handle customer service, order processing, and back-office workflows — in production, not proof-of-concept.</p>
    <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary" style="display:inline-block;min-width:220px;">Book a Discovery Call</a>
  </section>

  <!-- The problem -->
  <section style="padding:40px 24px;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(215,161,61,0.08);max-width:680px;margin:0 auto;">
    <div class="section-eyebrow">The Problem</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">Most teams automate 10% and call it done</h2>
    <p style="font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;color:var(--silver-dim);margin-bottom:16px;">60% of B2B distributors have order entry automation. Most of it handles only the clean cases — structured orders from known customers in a standard format. The exceptions still land on a human's desk.</p>
    <p style="font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;color:var(--silver-dim);">Exceptions are where the cost lives. Customer service escalations, non-standard orders, invoice disputes, supplier delays — these are the workflows that consume your team's time and your margin. We automate those too.</p>
  </section>

  <!-- What we do -->
  <section style="padding:40px 24px;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(215,161,61,0.08);max-width:680px;margin:0 auto;">
    <div class="section-eyebrow">What We Build</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">Three automation layers</h2>

    <div style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);border:1px solid rgba(215,161,61,0.12);border-radius:6px;padding:20px;margin-bottom:12px;">
      <div style="font-family:var(--font-head);font-weight:600;font-size:15px;color:var(--silver);margin-bottom:6px;">Customer Service Automation</div>
      <p style="font-size:13px;line-height:1.6;color:var(--silver-dim);margin-bottom:10px;">AI-powered first-response layer that resolves standard inquiries, escalates edge cases, and logs everything — without a human in the loop for routine requests.</p>
      <div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--silver-muted);letter-spacing:0.05em;text-transform:uppercase;"><strong style="color:var(--gold);">Outcome:</strong> 60–80% inquiry resolution without human touch</div>
    </div>

    <div style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);border:1px solid rgba(215,161,61,0.12);border-radius:6px;padding:20px;margin-bottom:12px;">
      <div style="font-family:var(--font-head);font-weight:600;font-size:15px;color:var(--silver);margin-bottom:6px;">Workflow &amp; Back-Office Automation</div>
      <p style="font-size:13px;line-height:1.6;color:var(--silver-dim);margin-bottom:10px;">Order entry, invoice processing, supplier coordination, inventory alerts — we map the manual steps and replace them with AI-driven workflows integrated into your existing ERP or stack.</p>
      <div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--silver-muted);letter-spacing:0.05em;text-transform:uppercase;"><strong style="color:var(--gold);">Outcome:</strong> Operational cost reduction, measurable in the first 90 days</div>
    </div>

    <div style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);border:1px solid rgba(215,161,61,0.12);border-radius:6px;padding:20px;">
      <div style="font-family:var(--font-head);font-weight:600;font-size:15px;color:var(--silver);margin-bottom:6px;">Exception Routing &amp; Escalation Logic</div>
      <p style="font-size:13px;line-height:1.6;color:var(--silver-dim);margin-bottom:10px;">The hardest part of automation is handling what the automation can't handle. We design the exception layer — what gets escalated, to whom, with what context — so your team only sees what requires judgment.</p>
      <div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--silver-muted);letter-spacing:0.05em;text-transform:uppercase;"><strong style="color:var(--gold);">Outcome:</strong> Team capacity freed for customer relationships, not queue management</div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Deliverables -->
  <section style="padding:40px 24px;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(215,161,61,0.08);max-width:680px;margin:0 auto;">
    <div class="section-eyebrow">Deliverables</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">What you get</h2>
    <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:14px;">
      <div style="display:flex;gap:14px;align-items:flex-start;">
        <div style="flex-shrink:0;width:6px;height:6px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--gold);margin-top:6px;"></div>
        <div style="font-size:14px;color:var(--silver-dim);line-height:1.6;"><strong style="color:var(--silver);">Operations Audit</strong> — current-state process map with automation opportunity sizing</div>
      </div>
      <div style="display:flex;gap:14px;align-items:flex-start;">
        <div style="flex-shrink:0;width:6px;height:6px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--gold);margin-top:6px;"></div>
        <div style="font-size:14px;color:var(--silver-dim);line-height:1.6;"><strong style="color:var(--silver);">Automation Architecture</strong> — system design, tool selection, integration spec</div>
      </div>
      <div style="display:flex;gap:14px;align-items:flex-start;">
        <div style="flex-shrink:0;width:6px;height:6px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--gold);margin-top:6px;"></div>
        <div style="font-size:14px;color:var(--silver-dim);line-height:1.6;"><strong style="color:var(--silver);">Production Build</strong> — deployed, tested, and running in your environment</div>
      </div>
      <div style="display:flex;gap:14px;align-items:flex-start;">
        <div style="flex-shrink:0;width:6px;height:6px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--gold);margin-top:6px;"></div>
        <div style="font-size:14px;color:var(--silver-dim);line-height:1.6;"><strong style="color:var(--silver);">Operations Playbook</strong> — documentation your team can run without us</div>
      </div>
      <div style="display:flex;gap:14px;align-items:flex-start;">
        <div style="flex-shrink:0;width:6px;height:6px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--gold);margin-top:6px;"></div>
        <div style="font-size:14px;color:var(--silver-dim);line-height:1.6;"><strong style="color:var(--silver);">90-Day Review</strong> — performance check, cost measurement, next-stage planning</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Who it's for -->
  <section style="padding:40px 24px;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(215,161,61,0.08);max-width:680px;margin:0 auto;">
    <div class="section-eyebrow">Who This Is For</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">B2B, B2C, and government operators</h2>
    <p style="font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;color:var(--silver-dim);">This service is built for organizations with high-volume, repetitive operational workflows — wholesale distributors, e-commerce operators, logistics companies, and government agencies managing large transaction volumes. If your team spends more than 20% of its time on tasks that follow the same pattern daily, we can automate most of it.</p>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(215,161,61,0.08) 0%,rgba(3,20,46,0.6) 100%);border-top:1px solid rgba(215,161,61,0.15);padding:40px 24px;text-align:center;">
    <div style="max-width:480px;margin:0 auto;">
      <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-head);font-weight:700;font-size:20px;color:var(--silver);margin-bottom:8px;line-height:1.3;">Start with the audit</h2>
      <p style="font-size:14px;color:var(--silver-dim);margin-bottom:24px;">30 minutes to understand your operations. We'll tell you what's automatable and what it's worth.</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary" style="display:inline-block;min-width:220px;">Book a Discovery Call</a>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
